## 3. System Overview

This document records the JUnit testing completed so far on the Spring Boot application class and controller package within the Academi Gymraeg application. The tests were created under the `src/test/java` directory and were executed using Eclipse with **Run As > JUnit Test**.

The application test checked that the Spring Boot application context loaded correctly and that selected application beans were available. The controller tests checked that selected controller classes were detected and created successfully by the Spring application context. The LoginUser controller was also tested to confirm that the login method returned the expected login view name.

Additional package sections will be added later after the model, security, and service tests have been reviewed and executed.

